<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>This is a very minor ZF coding standard issue, but affects svn diffs when we remove the 0x0d characters and then commit patches.</p>

<p>I do not recommend removing the 0x0d characters from library/Zend/Locale/Data/*, since that would result in "svn update" sending the entire CLDR data set.  Instead, I would purposely leave the 0x0d characters in these data files, and remove them when upgrading the CLDR data set (whenever this is done).</p>

